Brand



Brand Name: 



Jonathan Louis






Brand Description: 

Jonathan Louis started in 1985 with a dream -- to create a fine furniture line that would inspire people to use colors, styles and fabrics to transform their rooms. It was a passion shared by their team of employees, many of whom have been with the company for years, designing furniture from concept to construction.
Today, Jonathan Louis is internationally known as a fashion-forward brand offering artfully designed furniture that reflects today's lifestyle and delivers exceptional value, with practically limitless options  for customization. The company prides itself in offering artfully designed furniture that reflects today's lifestyle and delivers exceptional value. Their commitment to cutting-edge design continues in their current selections and in every upcoming collection of fashion inspired home furnishings. “Jonathan Louis started with a dream, they’d like to help you make room for yours.”




